description:
Adds 2 costumes based on young Plachta's and Ramizel's outfits from Atelier Sophie 2.

Featured costumes:
- All Grown Up
- The Usual Me!

Note: Costumes can be changed in the "Changing Room" from the diary on the desk in the atelier.
Please visit the official website for more information. 
This item is included in "Atelier Ryza 3 Season Pass."
name: "GUST Collaboration" Costume Set
